data.description: Enjoy this updated and rare 1600 SF condo in a private gated community and a secure building.  Featuring 2 large bedrooms, 2 full baths and an additional office/den, you'll have plenty of space to live in comfort and style. Tons of storage in the spacious primary bedroom with a walk-in closet equipped with an abundance of shelving! Unlike many other units, #409 boasts a large open kitchen with a gas range, breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Plenty of light through the multiple windows throughout!  The oversized family room has a cozy fireplace and access to the private balcony.  The washer and dryer are conveniently located in a separate utility room within the unit.  This condo is located in a well maintained building with an elevator,  garage parking with inside access and pool membership with Condo Association! Walk to Restaurants and Shops. Convenient Location. Great Place to Live!**Seller Loan is Assumable**
